{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-101","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> se često koriste u rečenicama, ali imaju različita značenja.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> se koristi za govor o svim stvarima u grupi ili kategoriji. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every student must complete the assignment</span> znači sve studente.</p>\n<p>Sa druge strane, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> se koristi u pitanjima ili odričnim rečenicama i znači jedan, neki ili bilo koji. Na primer: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Can any student answer the question?</span> pita da li postoji bar jedan učenik koji može da odgovori.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-101"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja je razlika između <span class=\"highlighted-text\">every</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> se ne koristi samo u pitanjima; <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> se ne koristi za sve stvari.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> za sve stvari, ne samo u pitanjima; <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> za jednog, neke ili sve.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> zote zinamaanisha kitu kimoja tu.</p>","feedback":"<p>Sve stvari imaju mnogo veće značenje nego samo jedna stvar.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> inamaanisha hakuna; <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> inamaanisha wote.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> inamaanisha wote, si hakuna; <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> inamaanisha mmoja, baadhi, au wote.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Every</span> se odnosi na sve članove grupe, dok se <span class=\"highlighted-text\">any</span> odnosi na jednog ili više, najčešće u pitanjima.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":4}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 101","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","dashedName":"task-101","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-102","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-100","id":"657e5d8f7f2274f2b1a8efcc","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-101"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}